00:09:22.519 --> 00:09:29.319
They provided the musical equivalent of JFK’s inspirational speeches, so these four young men

00:09:29.319 --> 00:09:35.699
from Liverpool were exactly what the country needed, they were a new emblem of youthful idealism.

