00:09:58.062 --> 00:10:03.839
Beatlemania had been going on in the UK since the previous year, since 1963.

00:10:05.299 --> 00:10:11.629
The band had been playing to sold-out venues and adoring crowds for much of the previous year, so

00:10:11.839 --> 00:10:18.999
it was only a matter of time before this infectious Beatlemania virus reached the shores of America.

00:10:20.319 --> 00:10:26.769
